Itri d [[tafekka tagnnawt|tafekka]] i d-ittaken [[tafat]] s usrag n [[azday aɣisan|wezday aɣisan]] aẓeɣlaw n [[Ahidṛujin|uhidṛujin]] i wfaris n [[hilium|uhilium]] deg wul n yitri ɣas ma deg kra n wamur meẓẓiyen kan seg tudert-is, s wanecta ad yebru i [[tafasa|tfasa]] i keččmen ɣer wul n yitri w ad teffeɣ d izenzaren ɣer [[tallunt|tallunt tuffiɣt]]. Srid mi ara ad ifakk uhidṛujin seg yitri, iferdisen yakk i d-isnulfan seg wezday aɣisan n uhidṛujin ttilin ẓẓay-it ugar n uhilium i d-yettwafarasen daɣen ama sɣur tamugri  taɣisant tatrawt neɣ s tamugri taɣisant deg [[supernova|usupernuva]] mi ara ad ṭṭerṭqen itran icafcalen s waṭas. Mi ara ad yaweṭ yitrr ɣer taggara n waddar-is (leɛmeṛ-is), yezmer ad yegber kra n ufimidi n [[tanga tamafsayt|tnegwa timafsayin]] akken i zemren imesnallunen ad akzen [[takura|takura-ines]] d waddar-is d tsuddest-is takrurant d waṭas n teskanin niden s wannay n unwiwel-is d umussu-ines deg tallunt d [[affaw|waffaw-is]] yakk d [[Aylalẓer|waylalẓer-is]], dɣa d takura tuɣridt n yitri i d amakaz agejdan n temhazt-is d twenza-ines deg taggara, ma d tiskanin niden am ukdu-ines, tuzzya-ines, amussu-ines d [[taẓɣelt|teẓɣelt-ines]] ttwakzen-d s umezruy-is, anda [[taẓɣelt]] n waṭas n yitran d tin i d-ittilin d a emgal n usfijjej-is, asesmel-a d win yettusemman s [[Ameskan n Hertzsprung–Russell|umeskan n Hertzsprung–Russell]] yettakez-d addar d waddad anamhaz n yitri<ref>"2MASS J05233822-1403022". SIMBAD – Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg. Retrieved 14 December 2013.</ref>.

[[Tugna:The Sun by the Atmospheric Imaging Assembly of NASA's Solar Dynamics Observatory - 20100819.jpg|thumb|250px|right|Tugna timedregt i yini n [[tafukt|tfukt]] igan d itri seg telmest n G amazrar, tafukt d itri yudsen yakk ɣer [[tagnit|tegnit]]]]

Talallit n yitri tbeddu-d am usigna i d-itteɣlayen seg tnegwa [[Asignew|tisagnawin]] igebren send n kra yellan seg uhidṛujin d uhilium d kra n yiferdisen iẓayanen niden. Mi ara ad yettwaẓenẓa wul atraw imir-nni kan ad yuɣal uferdis n uhidṛujin ɣer uhilium kra kra s temhalt n [[azday aɣisan|wezday aɣisan]] yerna ad iberru i [[tafasa|tfasa]].<ref name="How the Sun Shines">Bahcall, John N. (June 29, 2000). "[http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/themes/physics/fusion/index.html How the Sun Shines]". Nobel Foundation. Retrieved 2006-08-30 {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818063854/http://www.nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/themes/physics/fusion/index.html |date=18 ɣuct 2017}}</ref>, Ayen i d-igran seg wul n yitri ittaddam tafasa ɣer wuggug (lebɛid) n wul n yitri sɣur n urway n temhalin [[Azenzar|tizanzarin]].  Adad agensaw atraw ur t-ittaǧǧa ara ad yernu ad yeɣli ugar s ddaw n [[Taldayt|teldayt-is]],mi ara ad tfakk yakk tfasa n uhidṛujin deg wul n yitri ad yennulfu yitri s tkura yugaren 0.4 n tikkal n tkura n tfukt<ref name="Richmond">Richmond, Michael. "[http://spiff.rit.edu/classes/phys230/lectures/planneb/planneb.html Late stages of evolution for low-mass stars]". Rochester Institute of Technology. Retrieved 2006-08-04. {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904224040/http://spiff.rit.edu/classes/phys230/lectures/planneb/planneb.html |date=04 ctember 2017}}</ref> sin akin ad yettihriw alamma yuɣal d [[acafcal azeggaɣ]], ma deg kra n tikwal yettili-d usefsi n iferdisen iẓayanen deg wul d tissi tamaggaẓt i d-izzin i wul-is w ad yemhez seg yitri ɣer talɣa yefsin.<ref>"[https://web.archive.org/web/20080210154901/http://observe.arc.nasa.gov/nasa/space/stellardeath/stellardeath_intro.html Stellar Evolution & Death]". NASA Observatorium. Archived from the original on 2008-02-10. Retrieved 2006-06-08. {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618010901/https://web.archive.org/web/20080210154901/http://observe.arc.nasa.gov/nasa/space/stellardeath/stellardeath_intro.html |date=18 yunyu 2016}}</ref>

Deg wakeden-a, ul-nni yettuɣal d ayen i d-igran seg yitri ama d [[agezlan amellal]] neɣ d [[itri aneutronan]] neɣ ma meqqren s waṭas yezmer ad yuɣal d [[amruj aberkan]] 

[[Itri imisin|itran imisinen]] d yigtatrawen ttmagen-d seg sin neɣ ugar n yitran yeqqnen gugar-asen s teldayt, anda ttnwiwlen wa ɣef wayeṭ deg [[timezzit|tmezziyin]] irekden. mi ara sin deg yitran-a ur tlun ara (ur seɛɛun ara) timezzit yudsen, yettili-d usemdu meqqren n tsedmirt n teldayt ɣef temhazt-is i tlallit n tmuski s teldayt meqqren am [[agazu atraw|yiguza itrawen]] d [[amazellaw|imazellawen]]<ref>Boss, Alan (April 3, 2001). "Are They Planets or What?". Carnegie Institution of Washington. Archived from the original on September 28, 2006. Retrieved 2006-06-08.</ref>.

